Type of Feat: Class
Prerequisite: Black Flame Zealot level 1.
Specifics: On every odd level, the Black Flame Zealot progresses in one selected divine spellcasting class. If a character had more than one spellcasting class in which he could cast divine spells before he became a Black Flame Zealot, the player must decide which class to assign each level of Black Flame Zealot for the purpose of determining spells per day and spells known.
Use: Automatic.